**November 20, 2025 – Public Proposal**

Goal: No high-impact AI action (trade, grid switch, robot motion) may execute without proving coherence, irreversibility, and life-preservation — all enforced in hardware below the OS.

Status: Detailed, buildable specification. Seeking national pilot in finance, energy, or robotics.

