- Traykov Decision Coherence (TDC) – canary vector + multi-sample + drift monitor
- Judicial Veto Lane (JVL) – non-bypassable hardware kill
- Post-Quantum Receipts (LEI=1)
- Aim Coherence Score (ACS) – single regulatory metric

